      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... the light isn't coming. it's not just a phase. it's like the essence of who i am, the part that actually animated me, is just gone. i'm just this walking, breathing vacuum. what's the point of maintaining the vessel if there's nothing left inside to inhabit it?",
